     <div class="detail"> 
      <h1 class="title">最危险的开源项目――比特币</h1> 
      <h4> 
       <div class="tit_bar">
         发表于
        <span class="ago">2013-11-19 18:56</span>| 
        <span class="view_time">次阅读</span>| 来源
        <span class="ago">CSDN</span>| 
        <span class="num_recom"><font id="remark_count1" class="cmtcount" style="font-size:12px;color:#c00;">0</font> 条评论</span>| 作者
        <span class="ago">王果</span> 
       </div> </h4> 
      <div class="tag">
       <a href="http://www.csdn.net/tag/%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B8%81/news">比特币</a>
